## ğŸ”§ Techniques Used in NLP

To break down and understand sentences, NLP often uses:

- **Dependency parsing**  
  â†’ Looks at how words are connected (e.g., subject, verb, object)

- **Constituency parsing**  
  â†’ Builds a **tree diagram** (parse tree) to show the full structure of the sentence

